<!-- 制作方法 -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,5vw,2.5rem)] text-title mb-4">制作方法</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">在家也能制作美味的肠粉，跟着步骤试试看吧。</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <ol class="space-y-6">
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">准备米浆</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">将优质大米浸泡4-6小时，捞出后加入适量清水，用料理机打成细腻的米浆，然后加入少许盐和油搅拌均匀。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">准备馅料</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">根据个人喜好准备馅料，如牛肉馅（加入少许生抽、蚝油、淀粉、食用油腌制）、鲜虾（去壳去虾线）、鸡蛋等。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">蒸制肠粉</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">在蒸盘上刷一层薄油，倒入适量米浆，摇匀使其均匀分布，加入准备好的馅料，放入蒸锅蒸1-2分钟，至肠粉凝固鼓起即可。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">调配酱汁</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">将豉油、蚝油、少许糖、清水放入锅中煮开，制成酱汁；另外准备少许花生油和芝麻酱。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">5</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">装盘食用</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">将蒸好的肠粉用刮刀刮下，卷成卷状放入盘中，淋上酱汁、花生油和芝麻酱即可食用。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <img src="assets\images\food\changfen-making.jpg" alt="肠粉制作过程" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

