<!-- 制作工艺 -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,5vw,2.5rem)] text-title mb-4">传统制作工艺</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">每一只正宗广式烧鹅，都离不开这五步匠心工序</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <ol class="space-y-6">
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">选鹅与处理</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">选用120天左右、体重约5-6斤的黑棕棚鹅，宰杀后去除内脏、清洗干净，从鹅颈处插入气管打气，使鹅皮与鹅肉分离，便于后续上皮水和烤制。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">腌制入味</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">将盐、糖、五香粉、八角、香叶等香料混合，从鹅腹填入并均匀涂抹内壁，再用姜片、葱段塞入鹅腔增香，静置30分钟让香料渗透。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">烫皮与上皮水</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">用沸水均匀浇淋鹅身，使鹅皮收缩紧致；随后将麦芽糖、白醋、米酒按比例调成的上皮水刷满鹅身，确保每一处都覆盖到位。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">风干定型</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">将鹅悬挂在通风处，风干4-6小时（或用风扇加速风干），直至鹅皮完全干燥、呈哑光状态，这是保证鹅皮酥脆的关键步骤。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">5</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">炭火烤制</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">将风干后的鹅放入烤炉，用荔枝柴或龙眼柴明火烤制，温度控制在200-220℃，烤制过程中需不断转动鹅身，确保受热均匀，约1小时后出炉即可。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <img src="assets\images\food\shaoe-making.jpg" alt="烧鹅制作过程" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

