<!-- 制作工艺（非遗技艺） -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,5vw,2.5rem)] text-title mb-4">非遗制作工艺</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">每一只正宗虾饺，都离不开这六道非遗级工序</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <ol class="space-y-6">
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">处理虾仁</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">新鲜青虾仁去壳去虾线，用清水洗净后吸干水分，加入少许盐、白胡椒粉、料酒抓匀腌制10分钟，再加入少量淀粉锁住水分，确保虾仁Q弹。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">调制馅料</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">将腌制好的虾仁与鲜笋丁（或马蹄丁）、少许猪肉末混合，加入适量糖、香油调味，搅拌均匀后放入冰箱冷藏30分钟，让馅料更入味。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">烫制澄面皮</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">澄面与少量玉米淀粉按9:1比例混合，倒入沸水，边倒边搅拌至形成絮状，随后加入少许食用油揉成光滑面团，盖上湿布醒面20分钟。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">擀制饺皮</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">醒好的面团分成小剂子（每个约10g），用特制小擀杖将剂子擀成直径约8cm的圆片，要求边缘薄、中间略厚，便于包馅和蒸制。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">5</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">包制虾饺</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">每张饺皮放入约30g馅料（含2-3颗虾仁），用手指捏出10-12道褶子，封口处捏紧，确保蒸制时不漏水，造型呈弯月状。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">6</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">猛火蒸制</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">蒸锅加水烧开，将虾饺放入蒸笼（垫上油纸或刷油防粘），猛火蒸3-5分钟，蒸好后立即取出，撒少许葱花点缀，即可上桌食用。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <img src="assets\images\food\xiajiao-making.jpg" alt="虾饺制作过程" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

