        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">普洱茶</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">老广早茶“标配”，普洱茶口感醇厚，能解腻助消化，与虾饺的鲜甜搭配，让每一口都更清爽，尤其适合搭配多份点心时饮用。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
          <img src="assets/images/food/xiajiao-peiy2.jpg" alt="蛋挞" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">酥皮蛋挞</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">虾饺的咸鲜与蛋挞的香甜形成互补，一咸一甜，一软一酥，是早茶“两件”的经典组合，满足不同口味需求。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
          <img src="assets/images/food/xiajiao-peiy3.jpg" alt="皮蛋瘦肉粥" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">皮蛋瘦肉粥</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">绵密的粥底搭配虾饺，清淡暖胃，尤其适合早餐食用，皮蛋的独特风味与虾饺的鲜味相得益彰，是老广钟爱的“粥点组合”。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
